						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">mattmatteh wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">i noticed that it does the sprite dma twice.</div><br /><br />This is likely your problem.  Having quickly checked, it should only be writing to $4014 once per VBlank when the main game is running.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">does this game use nmi interrupts or polling for vblank?</div>
<br />
<br />Virtually all commercial games use NMIs because $2002 polling is unreliable.</div>

