						<div class="postbody">As I understand it, games poll PPUSTATUS ($2002) in only two places: <ol style="list-style-type: decimal"><li>while waiting two frames for the PPU to warm up after reset, and </li><li>while waiting for sprite 0 overlap. </li></ol></div>

